{"tid":2295404,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"智障香港人先會覺得有健康問題只能搵醫生","createTime":"2020-11-21T18:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T13:10:33.000Z","uid":342891,"like":8,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c9d1f02bbbc1b32a3758822078798ca91237a8","tid":2295404,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:36:12.000Z","msg":"醫生唔會識哂所有健康問題，醫生護士專職醫療各有自己的獨有診治專長，所以外國早就分家各自獨立診療。<br />\n<br />\n大量研究已經證實護士獨立診療疾病治果至少等於醫生很多時優於醫生，香港人被醫生用公權洗腦多年沒有國際視野，所以不明白睇健康問題不一定要睇醫生。<br />\n<br />\n連醫生都轉介睇其他專業，唔接受睇醫生以外的人應該睇睇自己智力有沒有問題，係咪俾醫生洗腦洗到有智力障礙。"},{"pid":"79c0ec1864aba3dc2a93d54ad931f66dc1596780","tid":2295404,"uid":204429,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:39:14.000Z","msg":"食左幾年保健品 一次都冇病過 feel到想病就食多小小c類supplemented 第二日就冇野 <br />\n利申 以前3個月左右睇一次醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be1e062ff3fe6b1016a1e7d367047a2569405de","tid":2295404,"uid":342891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79c0ec1864aba3dc2a93d54ad931f66dc1596780","tid":2295404,"uid":204429,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:39:14.000Z","msg":"食左幾年保健品 一次都冇病過 feel到想病就食多小小c類supplemented 第二日就冇野 <br />\n利申 以前3個月左右睇一次醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:40:55.000Z","msg":"外國的醫生好多時都會叫人做類似嘅嘢"},{"pid":"ee12fb9588bfabe35f305e18d5e738b72113ff5a","tid":2295404,"uid":236414,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:44:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f2c91d74cd7b54570612b935b05585b001884f8","tid":2295404,"uid":30079,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:45:57.000Z","msg":"莫非ching就係cu secret人人喊打嘅小wound nurse<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcab4bccfc0bf95ff9c72aba5917ec14d04bb44b","tid":2295404,"uid":342891,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2f2c91d74cd7b54570612b935b05585b001884f8","tid":2295404,"ui